DESCRIPTION:The WORDS = POWER exhibition will be available for viewing ever
 y Tuesday-Saturday through Feb. 28\, 2026\, in the Adams Gallery at the Gre
 gg Museum of Art & Design. WORDS = POWER brings words visually to life\, hi
 ghlighting emotional stories of beauty\, destruction and community resilien
 ce. The exhibition is a group show bringing together the following:\n\nNC S
 tate's Crafts CenterGraduate students in the Master of Fine Arts in Creativ
 e Writing Program in the College of Humanities and Social SciencesThe Afric
 an American Cultural CenterRegional North Carolina artists Carol Fountain N
 ix\, Meg Day\, Anne Storie Willson\, Katy Walls and Jaki Shelton Green
